OL,5, Nearly 400 drug driving cases have been
OL,6, abandoned because of delays in         
OL,7, processing forensic tests.             
OL,9,FSince 2019 police have been able to    
OL,10,Fconduct roadside mouth swabs and       
OL,11,Frequest blood samples from drivers     
OL,12,Fsuspected of being impaired by drugs.  
OL,14,FThe authorities planned to process     
OL,15,F1,000 blood tests a year, but demand   
OL,16,Fhas been double that figure.           
OL,18,FThe Scottish Police Authority (SPA)    
OL,19,Fsaid 386 cases could not proceed as    
OL,20,Flabs struggled to cope.                
